  "reference_number": "RUS1319",
  "remarks": "\nThe Secretary of State considers that there are reasonable grounds to suspect that Saodat NARZIEVA is the sister of Alisher USMANOV, an involved person under the Russia (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019. USMANOV was designated by the UK on 3 March 2022. As an immediate family member of USMANOV Saodat NARZIEVA is associated with an involved person and therefore NARZIEVA is an involved person under the Russia (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019. \nThe trust services sanctions were imposed on 21/03/2023.\n",
